  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们想画一个系统上下文图，展示我们那个多人联机版Cookie Clicker的核心交互。核心角色就是玩家，系统本身叫\"Cookie Clicker with Friends\"，重点是突出社交功能——玩家可以点击饼干、加入房间、还能实时看到别人的进度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Person",
        "System",
        "Rel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以这是一个C4的Context层级图。我确认一下：玩家这边我用Person类型，标注为\"Player\"；系统用System类型，命名为\"Cookie Clicker with Friends\"。这两个元素之间的交互关系需要合并描述吗？还是分开列？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Person(user)",
        "System(cookie)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "合并成一条关系线就行，文字写\"Clicks cookie, joins rooms, sees live updates\"，把三个核心行为都涵盖进去。另外图标题定为\"System Context - Cookie Clicker with Friends\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rel",
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建基础结构：创建了Person节点user标注\"Player\"，System节点cookie标注\"Cookie Clicker with Friends\"，以及它们之间的关系线。标题也已设置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Person(user)",
        "System(cookie)",
        "Rel(user, cookie)",
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我看看……玩家和系统之间的连线文字是不是有点长？\"Clicks cookie, joins rooms, sees live updates\"——读起来没问题，但视觉上会不会太挤？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rel(user, cookie)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确实偏长，但这是Context图的常规做法，用逗号分隔多个行为。如果拆分三条线会显得关系过于复杂。保持现在这样更符合C4规范，您看可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rel(user, cookie)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，规范优先。那整体结构就这样定了吧：一个玩家，一个系统，一条关系线概括所有交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Person(user)",
        "System(cookie)",
        "Rel(user, cookie)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认定稿。最终结构：标题\"System Context - Cookie Clicker with Friends\"，Person角色user（Player），System系统cookie（Cookie Clicker with Friends），关系线描述玩家点击饼干、加入房间、查看实时更新的完整交互流程。",
